source.description: Two-sided advertising insert for Laboratorio Dr. Domingo Plasencia's Yodelca (with iodine, arsenic and phosphorus) for lymphatic diseases, ganglion and lymph node tuberculosis, and Aditamina (vitamin A and D in fish liver oil) to aid child growth. Both adverts show healthy people.
